\033[1m\033[32mDEL\033[0m - Deinit a mango repository

\033[1mUSAGE:\033[0m
    mango @deinit [repo_path]

\033[1mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
    Deletes a mango repository by removing the .mango folder.
    If no path is provided, attempts to delete the repo in the current directory.
    Requires confirmation before proceeding with deletion.

\033[1mARGUMENTS:\033[0m
    repo_path    Path to the mango repository to delete (default: current directory)

\033[1mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
    mango @deinit
    mango @deinit ~/old-project